# Skill #7 - New Page Template

Skill Demonstration Challenge

---

## Instructions

### Objective

Demonstrate template for creating new HTML files 


### Steps

* Copy code from "https://unco-bacs.org/bacs200/demo/18 & 19" 
    * To "newpage.html"
    * To "article.html"
    * To "menu.html"
* Customize this file to meet your needs
* Use the stylesheet created for your home page
* Produce your own look a feel (do not use mine)
* Login to the Sensei Homework Dashboard and test your work
* Create a screen shot


### Requirements

Your page should have a unique version of these requirements

* Banner with logo and title and colored background or image
* Custom CSS file 
* Accent color for h1, h2
* Background color for full page
* Background image and surround for main area
* Custom footer with copyright signature


